<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Former Neighbours star Nicola Charles has revealed sordid details of what went on behind the scenes of the long-running soap.</p>

<p>In an interview with the Herald Sun on Friday, the 50-year-old actress-turned-author revealed a producer on the show once offered to pay for her to get a boob job. </p>

<p>Nicola appeared on the series from 1995 to 2016, and confessed the same producer also encouraged her to leak naked photos. </p>

<p>Spilling secrets: Former Neighbours star Nicola Charles has revealed sordid details of what went on behind the scenes of the long-running soap. Pictured on Neighbours</p>

<p>'I was patted on the knee in a very condescending way and told you can always leak photos of yourself after you wrap with the show to boost your image,' she said.</p>

